--  * 			select dbo.getParameterSettingDescription('{"descriptions":[{"language":"de","value":"Groupe T2i de default"},{"language":"fr","value":"Groupe T2i fr default"},{"language":"en","value":"Groupe T2i en default"}],"mapping":""}', 'fr') => return \"Groupe T2i fr default\"
